00:55:54,840 --> 00:56:01,320
folks in discussions, and also just doing the 
work yourself to get to the core problem and  

612
00:56:01,320 --> 00:56:07,680
helping people see that you're actually putting 
in your own effort and time to solve the problem.

613
00:56:07,680 --> 00:56:16,240
Yeah, and even just to riff on that 
second point, I think that there's this  

