617
00:56:32,200 --> 00:56:41,400
at least teams I've been a part of, where there is 
no job that isn't important. And so you as a PM,  

618
00:56:43,160 --> 00:56:48,680
I think if you're spending that time with someone, 
that means that you're learning something from  

619
00:56:48,680 --> 00:56:54,320
them and you're learning, having empathy for what 
they might be doing day in and day out, but you're  

620
00:56:54,320 --> 00:57:00,400
also pushing back and contributing and trying to 
