630
00:57:47,680 --> 00:57:56,240
And there's this thought exercise, this zoom out 
of, it kind of feels a little bit like if you're  

631
00:57:56,240 --> 00:58:02,000
all at a camp where you're trying to figure 
out, okay, where do we go send the scouts to go  

632
00:58:03,000 --> 00:58:10,440
take the rest of the camp and move things along? 
And there's definitely this inclination towards  

633
00:58:10,440 --> 00:58:16,400
executives and companies, especially broader 
companies, to do what's been working so far,  

634
00:58:16,400 --> 00:58:21,480
and that can often mean let's just wait and see.
And I think that's super interesting from the  

635
00:58:21,480 --> 00:58:28,480
concept of AI, there's this feeling of should we 
