641
00:58:58,120 --> 00:59:03,680
but then there's also this component of 
wandering and trying to figure out where  

642
00:59:03,680 --> 00:59:11,000
should we go? Where should we take the team?
And to me, I actually think the role of a PM  

643
00:59:11,000 --> 00:59:17,840
is to be that wanderer. And I have this story 
of, there was this moment in the company's  

644
00:59:17,840 --> 00:59:23,880
history where I was grabbing a beer with one 
of our engineering managers and he was like,  

645
00:59:23,880 --> 00:59:29,560
look man, I'd show up and I'm like, maybe I 
wasn't bringing 100% of my energy at this end  

