the next part of the company. And that part  

655
01:00:21,280 --> 01:00:27,040
was really tough, but I actually think that's 
where, to an earlier part of the discussion,  

656
01:00:27,040 --> 01:00:34,760
where an AI PM can really stand out is in being 
a natural wanderer and naturally feeling a little  

657
01:00:34,760 --> 01:00:41,240
